## Requirements

- Python 3.9+
- Apache Airflow 2.7+ (with native OpenLineage support)
- [Correlator](https://github.com/correlator-io/correlator)

**Airflow Compatibility:**

- Tested with Airflow 2.7+
- Uses Airflow's ListenerPlugin interface

